---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Icarus Mods | ProjectDaedalus"
description: "Browse 490+ community mods for the Icarus survival game. Filter by author, search, and download."
rootPath: "./"
---
<style>
  .gold-line { height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #f1ad1c, transparent); }
</style>
<div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 md:py-10">
  <div class="mb-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-icarus-500">Icarus Mods</h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 md:text-lg">
      Browse and download community-made mods for the Icarus survival game.
    </p>
    <div class="mx-auto mt-4 gold-line w-48"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 mb-6 border rounded-xl border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-center md:flex-1">
      <input id="search" type="search" placeholder="Search mods..." class="px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-icarus-500 focus:border-icarus-500 focus:outline-none md:w-64">
      <select id="author-filter" class="px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-icarus-500 focus:border-icarus-500 focus:outline-none">
        <option value="">All authors</option>
      </select>
      <select id="source-filter" class="px-3 py-2 text-sm border rounded-lg border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-icarus-500 focus:border-icarus-500 focus:outline-none">
        <option value="">All sources</option>
        <option value="curated">Curated</option>
        <option value="nexus">Nexus</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <span id="count" class="text-sm font-medium text-icarus-500">0 mods</span>
      <button id="reset" class="text-sm font-medium text-icarus-500 hover:text-icarus-400 bg-transparent border-0 cursor-pointer">Show all</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hidden mb-4 text-sm text-center md:block text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
    Don't see a feature you're looking for? Go upvote or add it on
    <a href="https://feedback.projectdaedalus.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-medium no-underline text-icarus-500 hover:text-icarus-400">
      the Icarus Modding Upvote Page
    </a>
  </div>
  <p class="mb-4 text-xs text-center text-icarus-500">Click on any row to view additional mod details</p>

  <div class="overflow-hidden border rounded-xl border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 mt-2">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse table-auto">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
          <th class="p-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-icarus-500 sm:w-1/5">Name</th>
          <th class="p-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-icarus-500 w-auto sm:w-28">Download</th>
          <th class="hidden p-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-icarus-500 sm:table-cell sm:w-1/6">Author</th>
          <th class="hidden p-3 text-right text-sm font-semibold text-icarus-500 md:table-cell w-20">Version</th>
          <th class="hidden p-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-icarus-500 xl:table-cell w-20">Week</th>
          <th class="hidden p-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-icarus-500 xl:table-cell">Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="rows"></tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-3 px-2">
    <p id="page-info" class="text-sm text-slate-500 text-center sm:text-left"></p>
    <nav id="pagination" class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center sm:justify-end gap-y-1"></nav>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 text-sm text-center text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
    Want to see a new mod?
    <a href="https://feedback.projectdaedalus.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-medium no-underline text-icarus-500 hover:text-icarus-400">
      Submit or upvote mod requests
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="module" src="./assets/app.js"></script>
